OL,3,CGuernsey needs more regulation to
OL,4,Csafeguard elections, review says
OL,6,FGuernsey needs to address several
OL,7,Funregulated areas around elections and
OL,8,Fintroduce a candidates' Code of
OL,9,FConduct, an independent review has
OL,10,Fconcluded.
OL,12,FInternational observers of June's
OL,13,FGeneral Election, working as part of
OL,14,Fthe Commonwealth Parliamentary
OL,15,FAssociation, praised the overall
OL,16,Fprocess but have made nine
OL,17,Frecommendations to the States.
