OL,3,CGuernsey needs more regulation to
OL,4,Csafeguard elections, review says
OL,6,FAn example is given about alleged
OL,7,Fabusive online comments made by one
OL,8,Fcandidate, where there are "no clear
OL,9,Fguidelines or mechanisms to address
OL,10,Fsuch behaviour, unless it is raised
OL,11,Fwith the police as a criminal
OL,12,Fcomplaint".
OL,14,FA similar Code of Conduct has been
OL,15,Fsuggested for media coverage, so there
OL,16,Fare formal guidelines to lay out the
OL,17,Fresponsibility to produce fair and
OL,18,Fbalanced reporting.
