OL,3,CGuernsey needs more regulation to
OL,4,Csafeguard elections, review says
OL,6,FThe report also suggests measures to
OL,7,Faddress low engagement from young
OL,8,Fvoters, such as using social media
OL,9,Fmore widely and running education
OL,10,Fprogrammes in secondary schools.
OL,12,FThe review calls for a clear
OL,13,Fcomplaints and appeals process, which
OL,14,Fit believes will improve transparency
OL,15,Fand build public confidence.
OL,17,FIt wants other gaps in regulation
OL,18,Faddressed, such as rules on party
OL,19,Forganisation and the creation of a
OL,20,Fpermanent oversight body to hold
OL,21,Fpeople accountable.
