OL,3,CGuernsey needs more regulation to
OL,4,Csafeguard elections, review says
OL,6,FIn response, Deputy Sarah Hansmann
OL,7,FRouxel, President of the States
OL,8,FAssembly and Constitution Committee,
OL,9,Fsays: "When you are in a situation
OL,10,Fwhere there's a lot of crunching on
OL,11,Ffinances, you don't want to just be
OL,12,Fcreating an all bells and whistles
OL,13,Felectoral commission for the sake for
OL,14,Fit, so we're looking at exactly what
OL,15,Fit is, what it could do and how to do
OL,16,Fthat in the most effective and
OL,17,Fefficient way possible."
